# 6. API Standards

## 6.1 Base URL Structure

```
Production:  https://api.smartsupply.ai/v1
Staging:     https://api-staging.smartsupply.ai/v1
Development: http://localhost:8000/api/v1
```

## 6.2 REST Conventions

| Method | Usage | Idempotent |
|--------|-------|:----------:|
| GET | Retrieve resource(s) | ✓ |
| POST | Create resource | ✗ |
| PUT | Full update | ✓ |
| PATCH | Partial update | ✓ |
| DELETE | Soft delete resource | ✓ |

## 6.3 URL Patterns

```
GET    /v1/products                    # List products (paginated)
POST   /v1/products                    # Create product
GET    /v1/products/{id}               # Get product
PUT    /v1/products/{id}               # Update product
DELETE /v1/products/{id}               # Soft delete product
GET    /v1/products/{id}/variants      # List product variants
POST   /v1/products/{id}/variants      # Create variant
GET    /v1/products/{id}/stock         # Get stock levels
```

## 6.4 Standard Response Format

### Success Response
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {},
  "meta": {
    "request_id": "req_abc123",
    "timestamp": "2026-06-16T08:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

### Paginated Response
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [],
