# 8. Inventory Engine Technical Design

## 8.1 Stock Calculation

```
Available Stock = Received - Sold - Damaged - Expired - Transferred Out + Transferred In + Adjusted
```

## 8.2 Stock Movement Types

| Movement Type | Direction | Source |
|--------------|:---------:|--------|
| PURCHASE_RECEIPT | IN | Goods Receipt from PO |
| SALES | OUT | POS / Order |
| RETURN_FROM_CUSTOMER | IN | Customer Return |
| RETURN_TO_SUPPLIER | OUT | Supplier Return |
| TRANSFER_IN | IN | Inter-location Transfer |
| TRANSFER_OUT | OUT | Inter-location Transfer |
| ADJUSTMENT_POSITIVE | IN | Manual Adjustment |
| ADJUSTMENT_NEGATIVE | OUT | Manual Adjustment |
| DAMAGE | OUT | Damage Write-off |
| EXPIRY | OUT | Expired Product Write-off |
| OPENING_STOCK | IN | Initial Setup |

## 8.3 Reorder Logic

```python
def should_reorder(product_id: str) -> ReorderSuggestion:
    current_stock = get_current_stock(product_id)
    reorder_level = get_reorder_level(product_id)
    avg_daily_sales = get_avg_daily_sales(product_id, days=30)
    supplier_lead_time = get_supplier_lead_time(product_id)
    safety_stock = avg_daily_sales * safety_factor

    if current_stock <= reorder_level:
        days_of_stock = current_stock / avg_daily_sales
        reorder_qty = (avg_daily_sales * (supplier_lead_time + review_period)) + safety_stock - current_stock
        return ReorderSuggestion(
            product_id=product_id,
            current_stock=current_stock,
            reorder_quantity=max(reorder_qty, min_order_qty),
            urgency="critical" if days_of_stock < supplier_lead_time else "normal",
            estimated_stockout_date=today + timedelta(days=days_of_stock)
        )
```

